# Information Gathering

- Assets:
    - IP addresses (both IPv4 and IPv4)
    - DNS Name(s) associated with this Assets
    - Underlying Operating System 
- Systems:
    - What the system is used for (Server, Workstation, IoT device)
    - Which network services is it listening on 
- Vulnerabilities
    - Are those services running a vulnerable version
    - Does those services uses weak and/or default passwords 
    - Does those services are configured securely
    - Is the operating system running a version that has vulnerabilities that can be attacked over the network




- credentials: text file containing username with associated password (username:password)
- passwords: text file containing passwords that have been found, bruteforced or cracked, but not associated to any username
- username: text file containing usernames 